    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Agents encounter more than JSON — YAML configs, CSV exports, XML legacy APIs, and environment files appear in deployments and tool integrations. Knowing when and how to parse alternate formats, and when to convert them to JSON for model consumption, keeps agent pipelines flexible without sacrificing safety."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
