      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "JSON wins for API and LLM wire format. YAML wins for editable config. Parquet/Arrow for large analytics pipelines — convert to summaries before LLM. For agent tools, expose JSON interfaces internally even if upstream is XML/CSV."
          }
